description: Try our easy to follow Cheat's Chicken Fajitas recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Fajita,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Spring,Low sugar,Sesame free,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Chicken,Dinner Made Easy,Peanut free
name: Cheat's Chicken Fajitas Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 500g Cook chicken breast strips Mexican style
250g Prep Set Go sliced red capsicum

recipeInstructions.text: Heat a chargrill pan over medium-high heat. Chargrill tortillas for 30 seconds on each side or until golden. Transfer to a plate and cover to keep warm.

Meanwhile, heat 1 tbs vegetable oil in a large, deep frying pan over medium-high heat. Cook chicken, in 2 batches, stirring occasionally, for 5 minutes or until just cooked through. Transfer to a bowl and cover to keep warm. Add caspicum to pan and cook for 4 minutes or until tender.
Return chicken to pan and cook, tossing, for 1 minute or until heated through.
Top tortillas with chicken mixture and sour cream, then serve.
